<div data-role="page" data-theme="a">
		<div data-role="header" data-position="inline" data-theme="b">
			<font color="yellow">	<h2>订购成功,请坐等送货</h2></font>
			
		</div>
		<div data-role="content" data-theme="a">
			
			<h3>您的订单编号:<font color="red"><%=@shopping.id%> </font> <br/>
				<small>如需修改订单，请微信留言</small>
				</h3>
			<hr/>
			<h3>订单信息</h3>
		 <table data-role="table" id="movie-table" data-mode="reflow" class="ui-responsive table-stroke" 	style="width:100%">
		      <thead>
		        <tr>
		          <th>商品</th>
		          <th>价格</th>
		          <th>数量</th>
		          <th>小计</th>
		        </tr>
		      </thead>
		      <tbody>
				<% @shopping.shopping_items.each do |item|%>
		        <tr>
		          <td><%= item.product_name%></td>
		          <td><%= number_to_currency item.price,:unit=>"￥"%>/<%= item.product_unit%></td>
		          <td>
						<%= item.count.to_i%>
				  </td>
				   <td>
						<%= number_to_currency item.amount,:unit=>"￥"%>
					</td>
		        </tr>
		     <%end%>
		      </tbody>
		    </table>
		 <hr/>
				<div class="contact-info center">
					<h3>
					您的联系方式
					</h3>
					<p>
					  <strong>下单时间:</strong>
						<%=I18n.localize( @shopping.created_at,:format=>:long)%>
					</p>
					  <strong>姓名:</strong>
					  <%= @shopping.customer_name %>
					</p>
					</p>
					  <strong>联系电话:</strong>
					  <%= @shopping.mobile_phone %>
					</p
					<p>
					  <strong>地址:</strong>
					  <%= @shopping.detail_address %> 
					</p>
					<p>
					  <strong>送货时间:</strong>
					  <%= @shopping.receive_time %>
					</p>
					<p>
					  <strong>订单金额:</strong>
					  <%=number_to_currency(@shopping.amount,:unit=>"&yen") %>
					</p>
					<p>
					  <strong>备注信息:</strong>
					  <%=@shopping.remark %>
					</p>

				</div>
				<pre>如有任何其他问题，可以发送信息至我们的服务号，我们的小伙伴会尽快为您解答。</pre>
		

		</div>
		

		<div data-role="footer" >
		 <p>Copyright &copy; 2013 上理果园</p>
		</div>
</div>
